Changes Made: 
Checkbox: changed header and item choices; font style to italic; changed header and value column sizes
Radiobutton: changed header and items; changed header and column sizes; changed font to times new roman. 
Slider: changed color of handle, selection, and track high; changed handle shape to square 
Select: changed header and header columns; changed items and input mode; changed value columns; changed font style to oblique
